rewards.reward: For those who pledge $1 or more we will provide you with a profile picture for your social networking sites (posted below). You also have our sincerest thanks and appreciation. In recognition for your help in bringing this goal to fruition you will be thanked in the credits of the Compound: 89191 game.

For those who pledge $20 or more you will receive a Compound: 89191 clothing patch. Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well.  Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA.

For those who pledge $65 or more you will receive your very own copy of the Compound: 89191 video game. Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well.  Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA.

Those pledging $100 or more will receive a Compound: 89191 limited edition t-shirt. Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well. These shirts are a limited edition. Each shirt will be marked as a part of a limited set. For example 13 of 250. Once these are sold out they are gone forever, get yours while you can. Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA. \r\n\r\n**There is a limited number of  250 promotional shirts**

Pledging $165 or more will secure you a collector's edition of Compound: 89191. You will also receive an early released copy of the games soundtrack.Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well. Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA.

A pledge of $250 or more will get you your very own autographed copy of the collector's edition of Compound: 89191. This limited collector's edition will be autographed by all of the key developers of the title. In addition to the collectors edition, Evil Tree Studios will provide you with all of the D.L.C., downloadable content, for Compound: 89191.Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well. Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA. \r\n\r\n**There is a limited number of  250 autographed limited collectors editions**

A pledge of $500 or more will secure you a copy of The Art of Compound: 89191. You will receive both a digital downloadable version and a hardcover concept art book. Your hardcover books are a limited edition and will be numbered accordingly. For example 1 of 500. Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well. Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA.\r\n\r\n**There is a limited number of  500 copies of The Art of Compound 89191**

Pledging $1,000 or more will turn your likeness into an NPC, non-playable character, in Compound: 89191. Your likeness will forever be a part of the Compound franchise. In addition to becoming an NPC you will receive the model sheets of your NPC, the concept art of your likeness and a wallpaper for your PC of your character in an actual game play situation. These will all for a digital download and made available to you as they are completed. Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well. Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA.\r\n\r\n**There is a limited number of 50 NPC's available**

Pledges of $5,000 or more will have their likeness featured in the collector\u2019s edition I.D. Cards. But that's not all, in addition to the I.D. Cards your likeness will be featured in the promotional trailers used to promote Compound: 89191. These trailers will be used in/on game review websites, social networking websites, TV spots, podcast and other multi-media outlets. Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well. Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA.\r\n\r\n **This reward is limited to the first 10 pledges. **

This is the Grand finale! Pledges of $10,000 or more will be flown out to Las Vegas, NV by Evil Tree Studios for the official announcement party of Compound: 89191. During your three day two night stay in Vegas you will attend the announcement promotional party of the game, have sit-down lunch with the creators of the title and receive a tour of the inspirational locations the game is based off of. The announcement party will take place in the heart of the strip at select nightclubs in Las Vegas such as XS and/or Tao. Experience Las Vegas how it was meant to be experienced courtesy of the Compound series and Evil Tree Studios. Your pledge includes all previous reward tiers as well. Once the limited rewards are out of stock they will become unavailable to all tiers of rewards. Release date TBA.

-For individuals interested in pledging amounts greater than 10,000.00$ please email us at: contactus@eviltreecorp.com 

 **This reward is limited to the first 25 pledges and restricted to continental North America. **
